data.description: Motivated Seller says bring a reasonable offer!!  Charming home Sulphur!  This well-maintained Maplewood home offers 3 beds, 2 baths, and is tastefully updated.  Inside you will find granite counters in the kitchen which opens into the dining area, and neutral colors throughout.  This home offers a nice size kitchen and a dining area.  New fixtures and new vinyl flooring on the main areas of the home.  This home offers a large room with a closet that could be used as your master, a game room, 4th bedroom, office, or whatever you decide! Outside you will find a covered back patio and privacy fenced back yard which is big enough for all your outdoor activities.  New roof post 2020 storms.  Don't miss your chance on this one!  All measurements are +/-.
